data.description:
Welcome to your dream home! Located in a serene and picturesque neighborhood, this stunning 4454 square foot property is the epitome of luxury and comfort. Boasting six spacious bedrooms and 3.5 elegant bathrooms, this home is perfect for families of all sizes. The upper-level features four generously sized bedrooms, providing ample space for rest and relaxation. The lower level is equally impressive, with two additional bedrooms that can be used as guest rooms, home offices, or whatever fits your needs. The basement offers endless possibilities, with plenty of space for entertainment, hobbies, or storage. From the moment you step inside, you will be enchanted by the stunning design and modern finishes. The open concept living area is perfect for spending time with See ''more'' loved ones, while the kitchen has enough room to cook with the family. With the expansive backyard, this home is sure to impress even the most discerning buyer. Don't miss your chance to make this breathtaking property your own. 
Home includes new carpet. Irrigation water is $350 annually. Hoa includes a 7-acre park and a 7-acre arena. Workshop is 40 X 60sqft with a 16 X 60sqft patio; Ceilings are 14' with 12' door. Workshop includes power but no water. Workshop can fit a motorhome and 6 cars or 9 cars alone.
